{"tid":1934910,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國境外傳入達189宗 , 北京錄64宗成重災區","createTime":"2020-03-20T08:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T05:08:52.000Z","uid":25468,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4458e0aad1489af4f0f5f4607ed6c76cc1de5c","tid":1934910,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0htbk2h5yBK01WSwNZg3FUGmwdKCJlJzhOMn16UgkldXkvfW5OYyoxeHofJS8uf2wTOHlhLXpCMHwoKztMPSkx/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0htbk2h5yBK01WSwNZg3FUGmwdKCJlJzhOMn16UgkldXkvfW5OYyoxeHofJS8uf2wTOHlhLXpCMHwoKztMPSkx%2Fw644&h=52cee2be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸新冠肺炎新增確診個案前日首度只錄得境外輸入，而且多達34宗，總數增至189宗，北京成為境外輸入「重災區」，截至昨零時錄得64宗，佔總數的34%，前日單日更新增21宗，民航局、外交部、國家衛健委、海關總署及移民局昨隨即聯合出手紓緩北京防疫壓力，將今起至周日4條外國飛北京航線改至其他城市降落及檢疫。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n相關航線包括俄羅斯莫斯科、法國巴黎、日本東京及加拿大多倫多飛北京，今起一連3天會轉飛天津、內蒙古呼和浩特及山西太原，<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">乘客均須落機檢疫，證實無病徵方可搭原航班回京</span></strong>，行李亦需清關。另外，台灣昨再增7宗境外輸入個案及1宗本地感染個案，總確診數字增至108人。面對疫情持續增加及全面封關，台灣民眾開始搶購糧食及廁紙等物資，蔡英文總統昨強調，台灣各項民生物資充足，呼籲民眾不要搶購和囤積，並警告會重罰故意抬價人士。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%A2%83%E5%A4%96%E5%82%B3%E5%85%A5%E9%81%94189%E5%AE%97+%E4%BA%AC%E9%8C%8464%E5%AE%97%E6%88%90%E9%87%8D%E7%81%BD%E5%8D%80-2582qP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Fpc%2Farticle%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25A2%2583%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2581%2594189%25E5%25AE%2597%2B%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E9%258C%258464%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2581%25BD%25E5%258D%2580-2582qP&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBJq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=fb1a4282\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%A2%83%E5%A4%96%E5%82%B3%E5%85%A5%E9%81%94189%E5%AE%97+%E4%BA%AC%E9%8C%8464%E5%AE%97%E6%88%90%E9%87%8D%E7%81%BD%E5%8D%80-2582qP</a>"},{"pid":"2db5cf7c5dc8ee